        "body": "## 🧩 Title\r\n**Added Google OAuth 2.0 Authentication with JWT and Prisma Integration**\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 📝 Description\r\nThis PR integrates **Google OAuth 2.0 authentication** into the Alumni Connect backend.  \r\nUsers can now securely sign in using their Google accounts. Upon successful authentication, a **JWT token** is generated and returned, enabling secure access to protected routes.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 🚀 Key Features\r\n- Implemented **Google OAuth 2.0** using `passport-google-oauth20`\r\n- Integrated **Prisma ORM** for user creation and lookup in MongoDB\r\n- Added\r\n",
